name: customer_data
description: Contains detailed information about customers, including demographics and purchase history. Updated nightly.
raw_schema_for_ai: customer_id:INT, first_name:STRING, last_name:STRING, email:STRING, registration_date:TIMESTAMP, total_spent:DECIMAL, last_purchase_date:DATE, country:STRING, city:STRING, zip_code:STRING, is_active:BOOLEAN, notes:STRING

name: product_catalog_latest.parquet
description: Parquet file containing the latest product catalog information, including pricing and stock levels.
raw_schema_for_ai: product_id:BIGINT, product_name:STRING, category:STRING, price:DOUBLE, stock_quantity:INT, supplier_id:INT, date_added:DATE, is_discontinued:BOOLEAN
raw_query: -- ADLS query depends on access method (e.g., SparkSQL, Pandas)\n-- Example: spark.read.parquet("abfss://container@account.dfs.core.windows.net/path/to/product_catalog_latest.parquet").limit(100).show()

name: vw_monthly_sales_summary
description: View summarizing monthly sales figures, aggregated by product category and region.
raw_query: SELECT * FROM REPORTING_DB.FINANCE_VIEWS.vw_monthly_sales_summary ORDER BY sales_month DESC LIMIT 100;

name: application_logs_raw
description: Raw application logs collected for debugging and analysis. Partitioned by date.
raw_schema_for_ai: log_timestamp:TIMESTAMP, service_name:STRING, log_level:STRING, thread_id:STRING, message:STRING, exception_details:STRING, dt:DATE
raw_query: SELECT * FROM staging_db.logs.application_logs_raw WHERE dt = '2024-05-22' LIMIT 100;

name: marketing_campaign_images
description: Directory containing images used in various marketing campaigns. Files are JPEGs and PNGs.
raw_schema_for_ai: file_name:STRING, file_type:STRING, size_kb:INT, upload_date:TIMESTAMP (schema inferred for listing, not content)

name: orders_table
description: Base table for all customer orders.

name: supplier_feed.json
description: Supplier product feed in JSON format.
